      "updated": 1769004843493,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "This is not exactly a queue\nbut for simplification we are\nthinking it as Queue.\nWhat it is we are will talk about\nFor simplicity so that we can map things\nwith regular message queue explanation is\nin this way.",
